---
import Button from "src/components/Button.astro";
import Layout from "src/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <div class="flex flex-col text-gray-500 m-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
      <Button text={"GAME RULES"} hoverEffect={false} />
      <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-lg">
        <li>
          A TASK WILL BE ASSIGNED TO WHICH IF COMPLETED, THE PLAYERS WILL BE
          REWARDED WITH <b>MONEY</b>.
        </li>
        <li>
          IN MULTIPLAYER MODE BOTH PLAYERS MAY COMPLETE THE TASK TOGETHER OR IN
          TURNS. COMPLETION OF TASK BY A NON-PLAYER IS CONSIDERED <b>CHEATING</b
          >.
        </li>
        <li><b>MONEY WILL BE DOUBLED</b> AFTER COMPLETION OF EACH TASK.</li>
        <li>CLICK <b>END TASK</b> IF PLAYER FAILS TO COMPLETE A TASK.</li>
        <li>
          THERE ARE <b>NO CONSEQUENCES</b> TO THIS GAME AND PLAYERS MAY STOP WHENEVER
          THEY WANT.
        </li>
        <li>
          CASH REWARDS WILL BE <b>CONFISCATED</b> IF CHEATING IS INVOLVED.
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-between w-auto mt-6">
      <Button text="CLICK TO CONTINUE âž¡" href={"/start"} />
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
